        <iframe
            src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3119.3299692951373!2d-58.73344785680499!3d-38.5722485855907!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x958f97e697ee2729%3A0xc23b4910ac90ff04!2sCooperativa%20de%20Trabajo%20Coomuniccar%20Ltda!5e0!3m2!1ses!2sar!4v1674792418844!5m2!1ses!2sar"
